wmsLayer.description: This layer is tile six of a bathymetry grid collected on marine survey GA0345 and Autonomous Underwater Vehicle (AUV) survey GA0346 over the Caswell Sub-basin, offshore Western Australia. This dataset is gridded at seven metre resolution. The total dataset consists of nine tiles. The colour ramp for the WMS is stretched bewteen 60 and 450 metres water depth. The dataset can be downloaded at the following URL http://services.ga.gov.au/metadata-gateway/metadata/record/83696.
